Hati Kudus Yesus Church, Ganjuran. It engages with the nature coz it has no wall or partition. It adopts local architecture in Central Java, "pendopo". Feel difference of the atmosphere on Holy Mass. Beside this church, there is a temple of Jesus in local clothes!
